                            <div class="about_wrapper"><h1>Why Renting Luxury Cars Makes Sense</h1>
                            </div>

                            <div class="about-group">

                            </div>
                            <p>Most of us think of rental cars purely in the functional sense. They exist to get us from the airport to the hotel to the client meeting or family vacation destination. But what you may not know is that many savvy travelers take advantage of this opportunity to upgrade to luxury rental cars, experiencing vehicles that outperform the more practical cars parked in their driveways back home.</p>
                            <br/><strong>Why Upgrade to Luxury Rental Cars?</strong>
                            <br/><li>First, you may think it still costs too much per day to rent a Mercedes-Benz vs. a Ford or Chevy. The truth is that by picking the right day, booking in advance or even taking advantage of a last-minute deal at the rental car counter, you may find that you’re paying a few dollars a day more, the same price – and even in some cases – less than you might for a subcompact, value-priced vehicle. It’s all about supply and demand.<br/></li>
                            <br/><li>Second, you may get nervous that if you get in an accident, you’ll be liable for damages to a more expensive car. Fear not, as trip insurance products such as Allianz Global Assistance’s Rental Car Damage Protector provides primary coverage for collision, loss and damage up to $40,000. (One benefit of going with a travel insurance plan is that accidents won’t need to be processed through your own automobile insurance, potentially raising your rates.<br/></li>
                            <br/><li>With $40,000 as the price limit, we’ll run down some of the more popular luxury rental cars you can upgrade to in order to get a bit more enjoyment out of the open road (or airport commute) without sweating the decision to do so. You deserve leather vents and motorized cup holders – even for 36 hours – and now getting them is easier than ever.</li>
                            <br/><a target="_blank" href="https://www.allianztravelinsurance.com/travel/rental-cars/luxury-rental-cars.htm">Source of the article</a>
